    "Further comparison between \"The Good Dinosaur\" movie and \"Rio\" movie will be carried out for the other object properties including the \"isDirectedBy\" and \"hasGenre\" to calculate the overall object properties similarities.The inferred-based semantic similarity, denoted as Sim infer I x, I y, for given two instances I x and I y, is defined formally as follows:where M denotes the number of common object properties that are shared by I x and I y, Sim objpr i I x, I y is the similarity between I x and I y with regards to the i th object property (i = 1,2, …, M) and is calculated as follows:(5)Sim infer � I x, I y � = ∑ M i=1 Sim objpr i � I x, I y � M Sim objpr i I x, I y = (6) 1 L i l=L i � I x l ∈R(obj Pr i,I x),l=1 ⎛ ⎜ ⎜ ⎝ 1 K i k=K i � I y k ∈R(obj Pr j,I y),k=1 � Sim H � I i x l, I j y k � +Sim att � I i x l, I j y k � + Sim inf er � I i x l, I j y k �� ∕3 �,where R objPr i, I x and R objPr i, I y denote the set of instances (i.e.",
    "object property range) for I x andI y, respec- tively.",
